                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240114-186-off1047 t18240114-186-cd1048"></join>, a looking-glass, value 15 s.
            </rs>; the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18240114-186-victim1606" type="victimName">
                     Philip 
                     Crofton
                  <interp inst="t18240114-186-victim1606" type="surname" value="Crofton"></interp>
